Question: Write a summary (plot synopsis) of your favorite movie.
Answer:
My favorite movie, which is Almost Famous by Cameron Crowe, relates the story of a teenage boy who loves music and especially rock music. He wants to be a rock critic, the next Lester Bangs. One night, as he goes to a rock concert, the members of a rock band befriend him and invite him to follow them in their tour. The movie relates then the strange education of this boy in this world he fantasized, discovering love and adulthood. 